in less than an hour.

24:06.780 --> 24:09.283
We pick him up and we don't look back.

24:21.044 --> 24:22.421
Keep the car running.

24:33.849 --> 24:35.225
(SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY)

24:42.441 --> 24:43.442
