the best they can,

26:17.703 --> 26:19.997
but... they're girls.

26:20.080 --> 26:22.457
They don't know what it's like to be you.

26:22.541 --> 26:24.877
Every family is special in their own way.

26:24.960 --> 26:27.004
Happy families are all alike.

26:27.087 --> 26:30.507
Every unhappy family
is unhappy in its own way.

26:30.591 --> 26:31.592
Tolstoy.

26:31.675 --> 26:32.718
<i>Toy Story?</i>

26:32.801 --> 26:34.094
(CHUCKLES SOFTLY)

26:37.931 --> 26:40.058
Come here, Oz. Sit with me.

26:47.983 --> 26:49.443
I'll show you a trick.

26:50.194 --> 26:52.863
