if Oz spends the night.

29:04.411 --> 29:07.122
-Ivy.
-He'll be fine.

29:07.206 --> 29:08.332
Right?

29:08.790 --> 29:10.292
Absolutely.

29:10.375 --> 29:11.460
Come here, bud.

29:12.669 --> 29:13.670
Yeah.

29:17.299 --> 29:18.300
Let's just go.

29:18.383 --> 29:19.384
