31:20.380 --> 31:22.341
That's exactly what I've been thinking.

31:22.424 --> 31:24.676
How would we do it? He has an army.

31:24.760 --> 31:27.721
It's gonna be dangerous,
and we... we can't put Oz at risk.

31:27.804 --> 31:29.681
Ivy, you need to calm down.

31:30.933 --> 31:33.769
