33:42.147 --> 33:44.149
and I almost did it.

33:45.150 --> 33:47.903
And then I thought about you...

33:52.950 --> 33:56.662
and how you left me alone in there

33:56.745 --> 33:58.288
without a word.

33:58.372 --> 33:59.665
No visits.

34:00.832 --> 34:03.377
Not even a glimpse of Oz

34:03.460 --> 34:05.170
in all that time.

34:05.963 --> 34:09.216
They told me you were insane.
I was trying to protect our son.

34:09.299 --> 34:12.761
You were trying to take him away from me.

34:12.845 --> 34:14.263
Admit it.

34:18.809 --> 34:20.769
So, in that second week,

34:20.853 --> 34:23.856
I pulled myself together,

34:23.939 --> 34:26.692
pushed those
self-destructive thoughts away

34:26.775 --> 34:28.151
and turned my energy

34:28.235 --> 34:32.739
towards freeing myself
from the fears that paralyzed me.

34:33.866 --> 34:35.826
And it was...

34:35.909 --> 34:37.995
desperately hard.

34:38.078 --> 34:39.997
But then I realized...

34:40.998 --> 34:44.710
that those fears were filling a hole
I had inside me,

34:44.793 --> 34:46.753
and you can't take those fears away

34:46.837 --> 34:49.298
without filling that hole
with something else.

34:50.507 --> 34:53.010
So I chose revenge.

34:55.846 --> 34:56.972
On you.

34:58.432 --> 34:59.433
Ally...

34:59.516 --> 35:02.477
You tried to make me go crazy.

35:02.561 --> 35:05.355
You tried to take my son away.

35:06.732 --> 35:10.235
You let yourself be seduced
by the babysitter.

35:10.319 --> 35:13.906
And worst of all,
you let Kai into our lives.

35:15.991 --> 35:19.119
And I couldn't forgive you for any of it.

35:22.164 --> 35:25.918
But then the thought of revenge...

35:26.001 --> 35:28.837
mmm, mmm, mmm...

35:28.921 --> 35:30.380
that cured me.

35:37.221 --> 35:38.764
(LAUGHS)

35:40.432 --> 35:42.392
You think you're cured?

35:44.144 --> 35:45.437
(LAUGHS)

35:48.065 --> 35:49.483
I wish you were.

35:50.400 --> 35:53.111
Hell, this is the woman
I've always wanted...

35:53.195 --> 35:55.614
strong and assertive,
someone who doesn't cower

35:55.697 --> 36:00.118
at the sight of clowns,
or holes, or blood, or whatever else.

36:02.663 --> 36:06.667
But it's a passing phase, Ally.

36:06.750 --> 36:10.420
